*&quot;Louis Jean Pierre Vieillot,&quot; in Tom Taylor and Michael Taylor, &quot;Aves: A Survey of the Literature of Neotropical Ornithology&quot;, Baton Rouge: Louisiana State University Libraries, 2011.

