*UROP at RWTH Aachen University, Aachen (Germany)
*UROP at the University of Cambridge
*UROP at the University of Essex
*URSS at the University of Warwick
*OUR at The University of UTAH
*UROP at the University of Colorado, Boulder
*UROP at the University of Hawaii</text><links>
